Zig-zag, sidetrack, turn to a line, etc.

sdr> /program = C3B
C3B
sdr> heads square thru
| 4B>  3G<  3B>  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B<  1G>  2B<
sdr> boys walk girls dodge
| 4G>  4B>  1G>  3B>
| 
| 1B<  3G<  2B<  2G<
sdr> zig zag
| 4G^  4Bv  1G^  3Bv
| 
| 1B^  3Gv  2B^  2Gv
sdr> zag zig
| 4G<  4B<  1G<  3B<
| 
| 1B>  3G>  2B>  2G>
sdr> zig zig
| 4G^  4B^  1G^  3B^
| 
| 1Bv  3Gv  2Bv  2Gv
sdr> boys trade
| 4G^  3Bv  1G^  4Bv
| 
| 2B^  3Gv  1B^  2Gv
sdr> zag zag
| 4G<  3B>  1G<  4B>
| 
| 2B<  3G>  1B<  2G>
sdr> centers pass thru
| 4G<  1G<  3B>  4B>
| 
| 2B<  1B<  3G>  2G>
sdr> sidetrack
| 2Bv  4Gv
| 
| 3Bv  3Gv
| 
| 1G^  1B^
| 
| 2G^  4B^
sdr> turn to a line
| 3B^  3G^  2B^  4G^
| 
| 2Gv  4Bv  1Gv  1Bv
sdr> split sidetrack
| 2G>  3B<  1G>  2B<
| 
| 4B>  3G<  1B>  4G<
sdr> pass to the center
| 3G>  2G>  2B<  1B<
| 
| 3B>  4B>  4G<  1G<
sdr> counter rotate
| 1Bv  3Gv
| 
| 2Bv  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4B^
| 
| 1G^  3B^
sdr> single sidetrack
| 1G>  2B>  4G<  1B<  3B>  2G>  4B<  3G<
sdr> single turn to a line
| 1G<  4G>  3B<  4B>
| 
| 2B<  1B>  2G<  3G>
sdr> right roll to a wave
| 1G>  3B>
| 
| 4G<  4B<
| 
| 2B>  2G>
| 
| 1B<  3G<
sdr> three quarter thru
| 1G^  3Bv  4G^  4Bv
| 
| 2B^  2Gv  1B^  3Gv
sdr> split sidetrack
| 2B>  1G<  1B>  4G<
| 
| 2G>  3B<  3G>  4B<
sdr> left allemande
| 2B<  1G>  1B<  4G>
| 
| 2G<  3B>  3G<  4B>
sdr> promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> /exit
